extendedInfo.description: Rush hour's coming, traffic intensity is RISING in the city,make the flow going by stopping and accelerating vehicles crossing the road.Rules're really easy,hit or slide on vehicle to stop or accecelerate it,keep roads CRASH FREE.TRAFFIC RUSH'S BACK!V1.1apps2sd on android2.2,for large screen,backround changeable in optiona bug fixed

reviews.title: Difficulty
reviews.comment: The ios version by donut games is much better. At score 60 the car count triples and it is nearly impossible to get a score higher than 70... Improve this or get more uninstalls
